    <h1>The Stratocaster</h1>
    <h4>The Fender Stratocaster is one of the most iconic electric guitars in the world since 1954.</h4> 
    <p>
        Its known for its comfortable feel, bright tone, and incredible versatility.  <br>
        It features three single-coil pickups and a five-way selector switch, which let you create a wide range of sounds—from clean and sparkling for pop and funk, to warm and smooth for blues, and even sharp and powerful tones for rock.<br>
        Its lightweight, contoured body makes it easy to hold, especially for beginners, and the tremolo (whammy) bar adds extra expression for bends and vibrato effects. <br> 
        Because the Stratocaster can fit almost any music style, it’s a great choice for new players who want one guitar that can do almost everything.
    </p>
